features: 【Ethernet Splitter 1 In 2 Out】The 1000Mbps RJ45 Ethernet Splitter Offers a Simple and Efficient Way to Expand your Network Connection without Additional Cables. It Supports Two Devices, Allowing Computers or TVs to Share One Ethernet Network for a Router at the Same Time, Transiting Signals without Interfering with Each Other.

【1000Mbps Transmission Rate】The RJ45 Network Extension Connector Provides a Maximum Transmission Rate of 1000Mbps per Cable, Ensuring that Signals between the Cables Do Not Interfere with Each Other. Ideal for Situations Requiring Swift and Efficient Data Transmission. (Note: The Actual Transmission Rate is Subject to the Connected Devices.)

【Wide Compatibility】Compatible with Most Network Ethernet Cables, such as Cat8, Cat7, Cat6, Cat5, and Cat5e Ethernet Cables. It Features One Gigabit RJ45 Input for Routers, Network Switches and Other Devices, and Two Gigabit RJ45 Output for ADSL, Hubs, Switches, TVs, Set-top boxes, Routers, Wireless Devices, Laptop, Computers, Etc.

【USB Cable Power Supply】Plug-and-Play Setup, Simply Plug in your Devices without the Need to Install Additional Software. (Note: Powered by a 1m Included USB Cable, Cannot be Used without Connection.)

【Upgraded Design】Aluminium Alloy Shell, Compact and Portable, Stylish and Compact Design. Featured an RJ45 Standard Eight-core Socket for Stable Signal Transmission, and the Enclosed Insulation Module Design Ensures Enhanced Convenience and Safety.
